64-bit version:
---------------
- nasm -f elf64 syscall64.nasm
- ld syscall64.o --entry main -o my64syscall

System calls numbers are in:
/usr/include/x86_64-linux-gnu/asm/unistd_64.h

If you added sbrk, you will need to link libc:
ld -Map=output.map syscall64.o --entry main -o my64syscall  /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libc.a

